Package ohos.media.common.sessioncore

Class AVBrowserResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.media.common.sessioncore.AVBrowserResult

  • public final class AVBrowserResult
extends Object
    Represents the media item information returned from the AVBrowserService, which contains AVElement instances to sent.

    You need to call sendAVElement(ohos.media.common.sessioncore.AVElement) or sendAVElementList(java.util.List<ohos.media.common.sessioncore.AVElement>) to send the information to your application. If you need to delay sending the information, call detachForRetrieveAsync() before the information is returned to detach it from the media browser service. After the process of the information is complete, call sendAVElement(ohos.media.common.sessioncore.AVElement) or sendAVElementList(java.util.List<ohos.media.common.sessioncore.AVElement>) to send the information.

    Since:
    3
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Multimedia#MEDIA
